{{Rewrite|date=June 13th 2026
|There are multiple SPaG and tone issues, notable ones being: 

Note: SPaG issues and misspellings will be in '''Bold''', while tone issues will not.

* "-and will repeat themselves every 3.3 meters." This feels generally off, and can be shortened down to just "-repeating themselves every 3.3 meters."
* "They open up to a '''party''' cloudy sky-"
* "Entering '''Eden''' for the first time places wanderers in a marble corridor." The wording here can be improved, e.g. "Entering '''Eden''' for the first time will place one within a large, marble corridor."
* "-'''and''' produces and intense euphoric rush similar to heroin."
* "When applied on the walls, the paint appears to replace the walling with the same type, but now in that blue color." Generally confusing, could be explained better.

There are just ''some'' of the issues, and this template will not go into full detail. The CSS is also somewhat off-putting, contrasting badly with the editor and class template. Portul has also shown discontent with the level, saying he isnt proud of it anymore. - smalla

I'm going to add more to this since I had always planned for a deletion template here. This section will be about relevance:
# God does barely nothing
The entity is very good design-wise, but fails upon execution. Their only role in the level is being able to kick out people if they broke a rule <small>sorta simililar to [[Entity 41]]</small>. It does barely anything, for such a cryptic name.
# Linearity
The level is too linear. I may be wrong, but the first area we know of is just a single hallway. If not, then the 2 hours isn't a measurement for lenght. Even if the person stands still for two hours they end up in the main area? And why begin the page with the hallways? Even it refers the fields as the main area.
# Filler
The page has some bloat, which are useless information. The page even has a slight Chairagraph, present in a whole paragraph (besides oje sentence) talking about paint.
- Avian
